name: PushUpsCounter
0:
”Alexa, start push up”
”I want to do ten push ups”
”I am ready”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: push up
des: The purpose of this skill is to let Alexa help you count your push ups and you can focus on your training. The counting speed is in a proper rhythm. Cheer up will happen right after the mid-point. No prerequisite is needed and is suitable for all ages.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
